108
00:04:26,830 --> 00:04:28,400
I was working with Dave Underhill.

109
00:04:28,460 --> 00:04:32,660
Ooh, "Dave." Sounds like Leonard's got a new BFF.

110
00:04:32,730 --> 00:04:34,930
Actually, he's pretty cool.

111
