245
00:09:53,160 --> 00:09:54,100
Okay. Let's go.

246
00:09:54,160 --> 00:09:55,100
All right.

247
00:09:55,160 --> 00:09:56,460
See you tomorrow, Leonard.

248
00:09:56,530 --> 00:09:58,460
See ya. 'Bye, Penny.

249
00:09:58,530 --> 00:10:00,100
Have fun.

250
